  <summary date="2020-06-22T21:21:23Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Metastatic Breast Cancer Access to Care Act

This bill exempts individuals with metastatic breast cancer from certain waiting periods for disability insurance benefits under the Old-Age, Survivors, and Disability Insurance program and related Medicare coverage.</summary>
